# Vue Frontend (`apps/web`)

## Components

```vue
<!-- ✅ GOOD — script setup + typed props -->
<script setup lang="ts">
import { ref, onMounted } from 'vue'
import type { Task } from '@/api/types/schema'

interface Props {
  task: Task
}
const props = defineProps<Props>()
</script>
```

- Use `<script setup lang="ts">` for all new components
- UI primitives: `@/components/ui/*` (shadcn-vue)
- Views: `*View.vue` in `src/views/`
- Absolute imports via `@/`

## Imports

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD — external first, then @/
import { computed } from 'vue'
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button'
import { taskApi } from '@/api/taskApi'
```

## Styling

Tailwind utility classes; group layout/spacing/typography logically. Prefer `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional classes.

## API calls in views

Decode with Effect schemas; run promises via `runRequest` or store wrappers — do not call `fetch` directly in views.

```typescript
// ❌ BAD
const res = await fetch('/api/task')

// ✅ GOOD
import { runRequest } from '@/api/base/client'
const tasks = await runRequest(taskApi.getAll())
```
